snippet.title: Crysis - Core-X Trailer
snippet.description: This is included on the Special edition disk of Crysis. It was developed in 2005 by Blur Studios, as a reference point for Crytek to base the game's graphics on. 2 Years later Crysis was born, and (with a custom config) far exceeded the quality of this video. Enjoy!
